[00:11.68]Light breaks through the galaxy floor,
[00:16.90]A twin sun rising, adventure calls once more
[00:22.12]Your laugh echoes across the stars,
[00:27.34]Two shadows chasing fate afar
[00:32.56]We ran through forests, leaves beneath our feet,
[00:37.78]Caught baby Rancors in a daring feat
[00:43.01]Lightsabers hum in a sunlit glade,
[00:48.23]Training as Jedi, our fears allayed
[00:53.45]Every jump, every fall, every leap we take,
[00:58.67]Dreams of kyber crystals and paths we make
[01:03.89]If the darkness calls, you’ll hold my hand,
[01:09.11]If I stumble, you’ll help me stand
[01:14.33]Side by side, through trials untold,
[01:19.55]Together we’re fearless, together we’re bold
[01:24.78]Little brother, across the stars,
[01:30.00]We fought through worlds, we healed our scars
[01:35.22]Krayt Dragons roaring, pearls to claim,
[01:40.44]Every battle lighting our names
[01:45.66]From shared rooms to galaxies wide,
[01:50.88]I watched you grow…a Jedi by my side
[01:56.10]Rockets and ramps, flying leaves like spells,
[02:01.32]Counting victories where the empire dwells
[02:06.54]Lightsabers clashing in twin-sun skies,
[02:11.77]Every adventure with wonder in your eyes
[02:16.99]Capturing beasts, uncovering lore,
[02:22.21]Kyber crystals shining on the floor
[02:27.43]Working together, through shadow and light,
[02:32.65]Learning the Force, embracing the fight
[02:37.87]No matter how far the stars may bend,
[02:43.09]You were my story, my beginning, my end
[02:48.31]Little brother, feel the Force,
[02:53.54]Guiding our steps on this endless course
[02:58.76]Baby Rancors tamed, Krayt Dragons slain,
[03:03.98]Kyber crystals found in the desert plains
[03:09.20]From shared dreams to the man you’ve become,
[03:14.42]I watched you rise… my Jedi, my brother
[03:19.64]Now you wield your saber true,
[03:24.86]A husband, a father, and hero too
[03:30.08]The galaxy wide, yet you remain
[03:35.31]That same bright spark, my twin flame
[03:40.53]Time keeps spinning, but I know,
[03:45.75]Through every star, you’ll never walk alone
[03:50.97]Little brother, soar beyond,
[03:56.19]Through suns and moons, your legacy shines on
[04:01.41]Every duel, every quest, every trial you own,
[04:06.63]Proof of how far our Force has grown
[04:11.85]Through all the worlds, and every fight we choose,
[04:17.08]I’m proud of you… always with you
[04:22.30]Two shadows fade into the starlight,
[04:27.52]Different worlds, same bond burning bright
[04:32.74]Little brother…
[04:37.96]I watched you grow…
